#compdef mcphub
# Documentation: https://github.com/ravitemer/mcp-hub
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-19
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.
# Note: the canonical binary is `mcp-hub` (node, ravitemer/mcp-hub); there is
# no upstream-documented `mcphub` CLI. STUB completion: only the help/version
# flags are accepted unambiguously across forks. Run `mcphub --help` against
# your installed binary for any vendor-specific flags.

_arguments -s -S \
  '(- *)'{-h,--help}'[show help]' \
  '(- *)--version[show version]' \
  '*::arg:_default'
